34
00:02:25,577 --> 00:02:29,604
藏匿著
stowed with riches beyond imagination--

35
00:02:29,649 --> 00:02:32,911
自上千個星球掠奪來的巨大財富
the loot of a thousand worlds...

36
00:02:32,949 --> 00:02:35,884
星銀島 星銀島
Treasure Planet.

37
