How'd he swoop in out of nowhere and vanished without a trace?

40
00:02:49,263 --> 00:02:51,355
我不知道
I have no idea.

41
00:02:51,398 --> 00:02:53,389
過來，快快快
Come here, you, you li--

42
00:02:53,433 --> 00:02:55,024
我要吹了！哦！
I'm gonna get--oh!

43
00:02:57,102 --> 00:03:01,800
好了，該睡覺了
OK, now it's time for this

44
00:03:01,838 --> 00:03:04,569
