我知道那是真的
I know it's real.

48
00:03:13,082 --> 00:03:16,210
好好，你說得對，那是真的
You win. It's real.

49
00:03:17,586 --> 00:03:20,179
-晚安，媽媽！ -晚安，寶貝！
-Nighty-night, Mom. -Nighty-night, sweetheart.

50
00:03:22,156 --> 00:03:23,520
我愛你！
I love you.

51
00:03:23,556 --> 00:03:24,955
我也愛你！
Love you, too.

52
00:03:30,628 --> 00:03:33,722
旁白：夜晚，伊塞林的風
There are nights when the winds of the Etherium...

53
00:03:33,764 --> 00:03:38,097
自由自在的飛舞著
so inviting in their promise of flight and freedom...

54
00:03:38,134 --> 00:03:41,467
令每個人情緒激昂！
made one's spirit soar!

55
00:03:44,506 --> 00:03:48,144
十二年後

56
00:04:11,228 --> 00:04:14,094
呀－呼！
Yaaaa-hoo!

57
00:04:24,404 --> 00:04:25,894
嗚呼——！
Whoo!

58
00:04:32,978 --> 00:04:34,605
加速！
Come on!

59
00:04:36,181 --> 00:04:38,240
嗚呼——！哈哈哈哈！
Whoo! Ha ha ha!

60
00:04:38,283 --> 00:04:40,250
嗚呼——！
Whoo-hoo!

61
00:04:48,457 --> 00:04:50,014
哦！我的天！
Oh, great.

62
00:04:51,479 --> 00:04:52,732
（旅館）

63
00:04:57,992 --> 00:04:59,855
霍金斯夫人！
Mrs. Hawkins!

64
00:04:59,892 --> 00:05:02,122
來了－ 把果汁裝滿
I know-- refill on the purp juice.

65
00:05:02,161 --> 00:05:03,491
馬上就來！敦萊蒂夫人！
Coming right up, Mrs. Dunwiddie.

66
00:05:03,528 --> 00:05:06,155
上菜了，四份玻璃球粉
There we go. That's four powdered spheroids...

67
00:05:06,197 --> 00:05:08,995
兩份月蝕。 還有一大碗
two lunar eclipses, and it's a big bowl...

68
00:05:09,033 --> 00:05:11,297
澤勒林果凍蟲，給這個大男孩的！
of Zorellian jelly worms for the big boy!

69
00:05:11,335 --> 00:05:13,495
-太好了！ -慢用！
-Awesome! -Enjoy.

70
00:05:15,939 --> 00:05:19,465
對不起，德爾波特！ 今天早上這裏鬧哄哄的.
Sorry, Delbert. It's been a madhouse here all morning.

71
00:05:19,508 --> 00:05:20,804
沒事，莎拉！
No problem, Sarah.

72
00:05:20,841 --> 00:05:24,470
啊，我的加種子的阿爾伯尼雜燴
Ah! My Alponian chowder with the extra solara seed.

73
00:05:24,512 --> 00:05:26,309
呣——！
Mmm! Yum!

74
00:05:27,881 --> 00:05:29,610
你好啊！
Hello.

75
00:05:30,749 --> 00:05:32,217
你從哪來？
What brings you here...

76
00:05:32,251 --> 00:05:34,310
好奇的小傢伙？
curious little...one?

77
00:05:40,592 --> 00:05:42,285
走吧！
Go away.

78
00:05:42,325 --> 00:05:44,260
你爸媽呢？
Are your parents around?

79
00:05:45,396 --> 00:05:47,885
怎麼了？ 啞巴了？呀——！
What's the matter? Cat got your--yaah!

80
00:05:49,364 --> 00:05:51,992
歐，這年紀的孩子真可愛！
Oh, they're so adorable at that age.

81
00:05:52,034 --> 00:05:54,125
歐，是的！真可惜
Oh, yes...deplorable.

82
00:05:54,168 --> 00:05:56,068
哦，是可愛！呣！
Uh...adorable! Hmm.

83
00:05:56,104 --> 00:05:58,594
說起這個 吉姆怎麼樣了？
Speaking of which, how's Jim doing?

84
00:05:58,639 --> 00:06:01,698
好多了。我知道年初
Much better. I know he had some rough spots...

85
00:06:01,741 --> 00:06:04,005
他受到打擊。 但我想
earlier this year, but I really think...

86
00:06:04,044 --> 00:06:05,634
他會度過難關的！
that he's starting to turn a corner.

87
00:06:05,677 --> 00:06:07,508
霍金斯夫人？
Mrs. Hawkins?

88
00:06:07,546 --> 00:06:08,842
吉姆！
Jim!

89
00:06:08,879 --> 00:06:10,779
哦，看來還沒完
Ooh...wrong turn.

90
00:06:10,815 --> 00:06:12,578
好了，謝謝你們送我回來！
OK. Thanks for the lift, guys.

91
00:06:12,617 --> 00:06:14,346
別急！
Not so fast.

92
00:06:14,385 --> 00:06:16,011
我們發現您的兒子
We apprehended your son operating...

93
00:06:16,053 --> 00:06:17,643
在禁區裏駕駛太陽能車
a solar vehicle in a restricted area.

94
00:06:17,686 --> 00:06:19,779
違反了904條例中
Moving violation 9-0-4...

95
00:06:19,822 --> 00:06:22,689
第15節
section fifteen,

96
00:06:22,725 --> 00:06:23,850
第6？
Six?

97
00:06:23,891 --> 00:06:25,359
-謝謝！ -不客氣！
-Thank you. -Don't mention it.

98
00:06:25,393 --> 00:06:27,520
-吉姆！ --您知道的
-Jim! -As you are aware, ma'am...

99
00:06:27,562 --> 00:06:29,552
這是違反條例的
this constitutes a violation of his probation.

100
00:06:29,597 --> 00:06:33,259
是的，是的！不！我明白。 呣，我們是不是可以....
Yes, yes. No, I understand. Um, but could we just--

101
00:06:33,299 --> 00:06:34,766
嗯，打擾一下
Um. ahem. pardon me.

102
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:38,293
長官，我是不是可以說一句？
Officers, if I might, uh, interject here.

103
00:06:38,338 --> 00:06:41,771
我是著名的物理學家， 德爾波特·多普勒博士
I am the noted astrophysicist Dr. Delbert Doppler.

104
00:06:41,805 --> 00:06:43,239
你們應該聽說過我
Perhaps you've heard of me.

105
00:06:43,275 --> 00:06:45,537
不知道？嗯，我這裏有個剪報！
No? Uh, I have a clipping.

106
00:06:45,576 --> 00:06:48,272
-您是男孩的父親？ -哦！我的天，不是！
-Are you the boy's father? -Oh! Good heavens, no!

107
00:06:48,310 --> 00:06:51,370
哦！他是我們家的好朋友！
Eww! He's just an old friend of the family.

108
00:06:51,414 --> 00:06:52,846
退回去，先生！
Back off, sir!

109
00:06:52,882 --> 00:06:55,247
謝謝！德爾波特。 我會解決的！
Thank you, Delbert. I will take it from here.

110
00:06:55,284 --> 00:06:57,114
好的，莎拉，如果你堅持這樣...
Well, Sarah, if you insist.

111
00:06:57,152 --> 00:06:59,618
啊咳，以後別讓我這麼做了
Ahem. Don't ever let me do that again.

112
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:01,744
由於他再三違反15C條例
Due to repeated violations of statute 1 5-C...

113
00:07:01,788 --> 00:07:04,780
我們扣押了他的車子， 如果再犯
we have impounded his vehicle. Any more slip-ups will result...

114
00:07:04,825 --> 00:07:06,381
我們定會將他送進少管所！
in a one-way ticket to Juvenile Hall.

115
00:07:06,425 --> 00:07:08,222
-少兒監獄 -監獄
-Kiddie hoosegow. -The slammo.

116
00:07:08,261 --> 00:07:11,888
謝謝長官！ 以後不會再發生了！
Thank you, officers. It won't happen again.

117
00:07:11,930 --> 00:07:13,487
我們會時刻監視著他
We see his type all the time, ma'am.

118
00:07:13,531 --> 00:07:15,022
-錯誤的選擇. -終結者！
-Wrong choices. -Dead-enders.

119
00:07:15,067 --> 00:07:17,034
失敗者！
Losers.

120
00:07:17,069 --> 00:07:19,298
-好自為之！ -我們走！
-You take care now. -Let's motor.

121
00:07:26,309 --> 00:07:29,243
吉姆，我早就跟你說過了！
Jim, I have had it.

122
00:07:29,278 --> 00:07:31,574
你真的想去少管所？ 是不是？
Do you want to go to Juvenile Hall? Is that it?

123
00:07:32,712 --> 00:07:34,976
吉姆？
Jim?

124
00:07:35,016 --> 00:07:36,641
吉姆，看著我！
Jim, look at me.

125
00:07:36,683 --> 00:07:38,673
我辛辛苦苦維持這個旅館
It's been hard enough keeping this place...

126
00:07:38,717 --> 00:07:40,582
全是我一個人忙呼， 你做過什麼？
afloat by myself without you going--

127
00:07:40,620 --> 00:07:42,813
媽媽，別大驚小怪的！ 一直都是你一個人！
Mom, it's no big deal. There was nobody around.

128
00:07:42,854 --> 00:07:45,551
那些警察只是把我的車子拿走了
Those cops just won't get off my--

129
00:07:47,991 --> 00:07:49,389
算了吧
Forget it.

130
00:07:49,426 --> 00:07:52,156
霍金斯夫人！我的果汁！
Mrs. Hawkins! My juice!

131
00:07:52,196 --> 00:07:54,594
知道，我馬上來！ 敦萊蒂夫人！
Yes, I'll be right there, Mrs. Dunwiddie.

132
00:07:54,629 --> 00:07:56,426
吉姆，我只是不想看到你...
Jim, I just don't want to see you...

133
00:07:56,465 --> 00:07:59,592
放棄自己的將來
throw away your entire future.

134
00:08:01,635 --> 00:08:03,569
將來, 什麼將來？
Yeah, what future?

135
00:08:14,714 --> 00:08:17,703
難以想像你是怎麼維持下來的，莎拉
I really don't know how you manage it. Sarah.

136
00:08:17,747 --> 00:08:20,477
要經營生意， 還要帶大一個像
Trying to run a business while raising a felon like--

137
00:08:20,518 --> 00:08:24,351
像吉姆這樣的孩子
felon...fellow... fellow like Jim.

138
00:08:24,386 --> 00:08:27,254
維持？ 我已經沒辦法了
Managing it? I'm at the end of my rope.

139
00:08:27,289 --> 00:08:29,189
對他父親的離開
Ever since his father left...

140
00:08:29,226 --> 00:08:32,715
吉姆一直都耿耿於懷
well. Jim's just never recovered.

141
00:08:32,759 --> 00:08:34,990
你知道他有多聰明的
And you know how smart he is.

142
00:08:35,028 --> 00:08:39,054
他八歲的時候 做了第一個太陽能滑板
He built his first solar surfer when he was eight!

143
00:08:39,099 --> 00:08:41,531
之後，他就沒上過學
And yet. he's failing at school...

144
00:08:41,567 --> 00:08:43,626
他不斷地惹麻煩
he is constantly in trouble...

145
00:08:43,668 --> 00:08:46,466
跟他說話的時候， 他就像個陌生人
and when I talk to him. he's like a stranger to me.

146
00:08:46,505 --> 00:08:49,302
我不知道為什麼。德爾波特， 我已經盡力了！
I don't know. Delbert. I've tried everything--

147
00:08:58,382 --> 00:08:59,847
嗨，先生！
Hey, Mister?

148
00:08:59,882 --> 00:09:01,781
罐子裏的先生，你還好嗎？
Mister,

149
00:09:01,816 --> 00:09:03,307
啊——！
Aah!

150
00:09:06,387 --> 00:09:08,014
他馬上來了
He's a-comin'.

151
00:09:08,054 --> 00:09:10,022
你聽到他說話了嗎？
Can you hear him?

152
00:09:10,056 --> 00:09:13,047
那些齒輪和陀螺呼呼的轉著
Those gears and gyros clickin' and whirrin'...

153
00:09:13,093 --> 00:09:14,753
就像那個惡魔一樣！
Iike the devil himself!

154
00:09:14,793 --> 00:09:17,693
哦，撞暈頭了？
Uh, hit your head there pretty hard, didn't ya?

155
00:09:17,729 --> 00:09:19,322
他來搶我的箱子
He's after me chest...

156
00:09:19,365 --> 00:09:23,697
那個殘忍的機器人 還有他的屠殺部隊
that fiendish cyborg and his band of cutthroats.

157
00:09:25,434 --> 00:09:27,061
但是他們必須
But they'll have to pry it...

158
00:09:27,104 --> 00:09:33,236
先從比利·鮑恩斯冰冷的 死人的手指中探察
from old Billy Bones' cold, dead fingers afore l--argh!

159
00:09:34,911 --> 00:09:36,376
哦，我的...
Oh, my--

160
00:09:36,411 --> 00:09:39,108
哦，來吧，把胳膊給我
Uh, come on, give me your arm.

161
00:09:40,447 --> 00:09:41,879
對了
That's it.

162
00:09:43,750 --> 00:09:47,810
-好孩子。 -我這麼做媽媽會很高興的
-Good lad. -Mom's gonna love this.

163
00:09:55,859 --> 00:09:58,988
德爾波特，感謝您聽你我嘮叨。
Thanks for listening, Delbert.

164
00:09:59,030 --> 00:10:02,226
我好多了
It helps.

165
00:10:04,633 --> 00:10:07,829
一切都會好的
It's going to be OK.

166
00:10:07,869 --> 00:10:09,633
放心吧
You'll see.

167
00:10:09,671 --> 00:10:12,333
我一直希望， 有一天我打開門...
I keep dreaming one day I'll open that door...

168
00:10:12,372 --> 00:10:14,999
他會像以前一樣
and there he'll be just the way he was.

169
00:10:15,042 --> 00:10:18,373
一個開朗、快樂的男孩， 抱著一隻新寵物...
A smiling, happy little boy, holding a new pet...

170
00:10:18,411 --> 00:10:21,073
讓我允許收留它
and begging me to let him keep it.

171
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:26,006
詹姆斯·普萊迪斯·霍金斯
James Pleiades Hawkins!

172
00:10:26,051 --> 00:10:28,280
媽媽，他受傷了 傷得很重
Mom, he's hurt...bad!

173
00:10:29,919 --> 00:10:31,979
我的箱子，小伙子
Me chest, lad.

174
00:10:36,124 --> 00:10:38,355
他馬上就來了
He'll be comin' soon.

175
00:10:39,728 --> 00:10:42,218
不能讓他找到這東西
Can't let them find this.

176
00:10:42,263 --> 00:10:43,593
誰要來？
Who's coming?

177
00:10:43,631 --> 00:10:46,724
機器人！
The cyborg!

178
00:10:46,766 --> 00:10:51,361
小心那機器人！
Beware the cyborg!

179
00:10:58,177 --> 00:10:59,335
哦！
Ohh!

180
00:11:11,987 --> 00:11:13,386
快！我們必須馬上離開這兒！
Quick! We gotta go!

181
00:11:13,420 --> 00:11:15,650
-哦！ -啊！
-Ohh! -Aah!

182
00:11:15,689 --> 00:11:17,815
我想這時候我離不開吉姆了！
I believe I'm with Jim on this one!

183
00:11:28,935 --> 00:11:30,594
黛利拉！（原是聖經中人物） 哈利路亞！
Delilah! Hallelujah!

184
00:11:31,801 --> 00:11:32,996
呆在那兒！ 別動！
Stay! Don't move!

185
00:11:33,037 --> 00:11:34,903
那東西呢？
Where is it?!

186
00:11:34,939 --> 00:11:36,564
把它找出來！
Find it!

187
00:11:36,605 --> 00:11:37,936
不用擔心，莎拉！
Don't worry. Sarah.

188
00:11:37,973 --> 00:11:40,203
我是個物理學專家
I'm an expert in the laws of physical science.

189
00:11:40,241 --> 00:11:42,299
-我們數到三。一... -三！
-On the count of three--one... -Three!

190
00:11:42,342 --> 00:11:44,833
-啊！ -啊！
-Aah! -Aah!

191
00:11:44,880 --> 00:11:46,506
快，黛利拉，快！
Go, Delilah! Go!

192
00:11:46,546 --> 00:11:49,879
快走！對極了！快！
Go! That's it! That's it! Go!

193
00:11:56,122 --> 00:11:57,316
駕！駕！
Hyah! Hyah!

194
00:12:11,253 --> 00:12:13,915
我跟警察說了
I just spoke with the constabulary.

195
00:12:13,956 --> 00:12:17,015
那些海盜逃走的時候 沒有留下任何線索！
Those blaggard pirates have fled without a trace.

196
00:12:18,559 --> 00:12:20,049
我很難過，莎拉！
I'm sorry, Sarah.

197
00:12:20,093 --> 00:12:24,188
我想老本鮑旅館已經化為灰燼了
I'm afraid the old Benbow lnn has burned to the ground.

198
00:12:28,668 --> 00:12:34,531
對了， 都是那個小球帶來的麻煩！
Ahem. Well, certainly a lot of trouble...over that odd little sphere.

199
00:12:34,572 --> 00:12:37,267
那些標記看起來挺奇怪的
Those markings baffle me.

200
00:12:37,307 --> 00:12:39,467
我從沒見過像這樣的東西
Unlike anything I've ever encountered.

201
00:12:40,678 --> 00:12:42,109
就是以我豐富的經驗
Even with my vast experience...

202
00:12:42,143 --> 00:12:43,610
和驚人的智慧
and superior intellect...

203
00:12:43,644 --> 00:12:46,738
都得花好幾年才能打開它
it would take me years to unlock its--hey!

204
00:12:49,917 --> 00:12:53,681
什麼？是張地圖！
Why, it's a map!

205
00:12:54,988 --> 00:12:56,180
等等！等等！
Wait. Wait, wait, wait!

206
00:12:56,222 --> 00:12:59,157
這是我們，在特雷斯普行星
This is us,

207
00:13:01,961 --> 00:13:03,985
那是麥哲倫雲層
That's the Magellanic Cloud!

208
00:13:04,028 --> 00:13:06,120
哦！珊瑚星系！
Whoo! The Coral Galaxy!

209
00:13:06,162 --> 00:13:07,254
哦！
Oh!

210
00:13:07,297 --> 00:13:09,424
那是天鵝星座！
That's the Cygnus Cross...

211
00:13:09,465 --> 00:13:11,899
克裏安黑洞！
and that's the Kerian Abyss.

212
00:13:11,934 --> 00:13:15,369
等等！這是什麼？這是什麼？ 奇怪，它是...
Wait. What's this? What's this? Why, it--it's...

213
00:13:15,404 --> 00:13:17,234
星銀島！
Treasure Planet.

214
00:13:17,271 --> 00:13:18,636
不！
No!

215
00:13:18,672 --> 00:13:20,606
是星銀島！
That's Treasure Planet!

216
00:13:20,640 --> 00:13:22,302
弗林特的寶藏？
Flint's trove?

217
00:13:22,343 --> 00:13:24,311
掠奪上千個世界的戰利品？
The loot of a thousand worlds?

218
00:13:24,345 --> 00:13:25,972
你知道這意味著什麼嗎？
You know what this means?

219
00:13:26,013 --> 00:13:29,468
就是說所有的財寶只是在一艘船上。
It means that all that treasure is only a boat ride away.

220
00:13:29,514 --> 00:13:33,043
有了它就有了全世界
Whoever brings it back would hold an eternal place...

221
00:13:33,086 --> 00:13:36,611
高高的站在萬神殿上受萬人朝拜！ 想必他就是這樣！
atop the pantheon of explorers! He'd be able to experience--

222
00:13:36,653 --> 00:13:39,054
哦！剛才怎麼了？
Whoo! What just happened?

223
00:13:39,089 --> 00:13:42,148
媽媽，就是這個！ 這是所有問題的答案！
Mom, this is it. This is

224
00:13:42,190 --> 00:13:44,420
吉姆，這絕對不可能！
Jim, there is

225
00:13:44,459 --> 00:13:47,019
您還記得那些故事嗎？
Don't you remember, all those stories?

226
00:13:47,062 --> 00:13:49,895
就是了，他們只是故事！
That's all they were--stories!

227
00:13:49,932 --> 00:13:51,057
有了那些財寶
With that treasure...

228
00:13:51,098 --> 00:13:53,724
我們可以建造數百個本鮑旅館
we could rebuild the Benbow a hundred times over!

229
00:13:53,766 --> 00:13:56,463
哦，這是...這到底是...
Well, this is--

230
00:13:56,502 --> 00:13:58,903
德爾波特，你可以解釋這個荒謬的事情？
Delbert, would you please explain how ridiculous this is?

231
00:13:58,939 --> 00:14:01,235
真是太荒謬了
It's totally preposterous...

232
00:14:01,274 --> 00:14:03,299
一個人穿過整個星系
traversing the entire galaxy alone.

233
00:14:03,342 --> 00:14:05,400
好了，現在乖乖呆在這兒吧
Now at last,

234
00:14:05,443 --> 00:14:08,071
-所以我要和你一起去！ -德爾波特！
-That's why I'm going with you. -Delbert!

235
00:14:08,111 --> 00:14:10,511
用我的積蓄來作為探險隊的費用
I'll use my savings to finance the expedition.

236
00:14:10,547 --> 00:14:14,005
我要搞艘船， 雇一個船長還有一個水手隊！
I'll commission a ship, hire a captain and a crew.

237
00:14:14,051 --> 00:14:15,346
你不是認真的吧？
You're not serious.

238
00:14:15,385 --> 00:14:17,979
我這輩子就等這麼個機會了
All my life I've been waiting for an opportunity like this...

239
00:14:18,020 --> 00:14:21,456
我聽到了一個聲音： 「前進吧，德爾波特！前進吧，德爾波特」
and here it is screaming, "Go, Delbert! Go, Delbert!"

240
00:14:21,489 --> 00:14:24,616
好了，好了！ 你們兩個都瘋了！
OK. OK! You're both grounded!

241
00:14:25,893 --> 00:14:27,791
媽媽，你看
Mom. Iook...

242
00:14:27,827 --> 00:14:31,354
我知道我讓這裏亂七八糟的
I know that I keep messing everything up...

243
00:14:31,398 --> 00:14:34,128
我知道
and I know...

244
00:14:34,167 --> 00:14:36,156
我讓你失望
that I let you down.

245
00:14:38,070 --> 00:14:40,833
但這是我向你證明我自己的機會
But this is my chance to make it up to you.

246
00:14:40,872 --> 00:14:43,532
我會把一切處理的妥妥當當的
I'm gonna set things right.

247
00:14:43,573 --> 00:14:46,303
莎拉？
Sarah?

248
00:14:46,342 --> 00:14:48,536
可以嗎？
If I may?

249
00:14:48,577 --> 00:14:51,011
你說你已經沒辦法了
You said yourself, you've tried everything.

250
00:14:51,047 --> 00:14:52,673
沒有比在太空中鍛煉的幾個月
There are much worse remedies...

251
00:14:52,714 --> 00:14:55,842
更好的補救方法了
than a few character-building months in space.

252
00:14:55,884 --> 00:14:58,679
你這麼說是因為 這麼做是對的
Are you saying this because it's the right thing...

253
00:14:58,718 --> 00:15:00,981
還是因為你真的想去？
or because you really want to go?

254
00:15:01,020 --> 00:15:03,749
真的，真的，真的， 真的想去
I really, really, really, really want to go...

255
00:15:03,789 --> 00:15:05,722
而且這麼做是對的！
and it's the right thing.

256
00:15:13,197 --> 00:15:14,390
吉姆
Jim...

257
00:15:14,431 --> 00:15:17,092
我不想失去你
I don't want to lose you.

258
00:15:17,133 --> 00:15:20,659
媽媽，我也捨不得
Mom...you won't.

259
00:15:20,703 --> 00:15:22,864
我不會讓你失望的
I'll make you proud.

260
00:15:24,438 --> 00:15:26,464
好了，哦
Well. uh. ahem.

261
00:15:26,508 --> 00:15:28,065
我們這不是在一起嗎？
There we are then.

262
00:15:28,110 --> 00:15:30,343
我們馬上開始準備
We'll begin preparations at once.

263
00:15:30,344 --> 00:15:30,743
我們馬上開始準備
We'll begin preparations at once.

264
00:15:30,777 --> 00:15:35,076
吉姆，我的孩子， 我們馬上要升上太空了
Jim, my boy, soon we'll be off to the spaceport.

265
00:16:15,646 --> 00:16:18,581
吉姆，等等我！
Jim! Oh. Jim! Wait for me!

266
00:16:25,254 --> 00:16:28,450
哦，吉姆，我們
Well, Jim, this should be

267
00:16:28,490 --> 00:16:30,649
應該好好的互相瞭解一下
for the two of us to get to know one another.

268
00:16:30,691 --> 00:16:33,057
你知道他們說什麼， 親情溝通，呣
You know what they say, familiarity breeds, um...

269
00:16:33,094 --> 00:16:35,060
這樣說不太禮貌 但是，在我麼看來...
well, contempt, but, in our case--

270
00:16:35,094 --> 00:16:39,190
走吧，找找我們的船！
Look, let's just find the ship. OK?

271
00:16:40,459 --> 00:16:43,915
-你右手邊的第二個泊位！ -你可以找到的！
-Second berth on your right! -You can't miss it.

272
00:16:43,962 --> 00:16:46,226
嘿，謝謝！
Hey, thanks.

273
00:16:46,263 --> 00:16:48,857
合適嗎？
It's the suit, isn't it?

274
00:16:48,899 --> 00:16:51,264
那個可惡的女店員！
to that pushy two-headed saleswoman.

275
00:16:51,301 --> 00:16:53,631
這個說合適！
This one said it fit,

276
00:16:53,668 --> 00:16:56,693
哦不知道該怎麼辦。 我都有些混亂了！哦！
I didn't know what to do. I get so flustered. Ooh!

277
00:16:58,040 --> 00:17:02,566
歐，吉姆！這是我們的船！ R.L.S.的遺產！
Oh, Jim! This is our ship! The R.L.S. Legacy!

278
00:17:06,345 --> 00:17:08,211
哇！
Whoa!

279
00:17:09,616 --> 00:17:12,641
把這些桶搬上去！
Stow those casks forward!

280
00:17:12,683 --> 00:17:15,152
拉上去！
Heave together now!

281
00:17:15,186 --> 00:17:18,018
太酷了！
How cool is this?

282
00:17:19,256 --> 00:17:21,053
對不起，我是說...
Sorry about that. I didn't mean--

283
00:17:24,960 --> 00:17:27,689
讓我來
Allow me to handle this.

284
00:17:35,836 --> 00:17:37,268
吉姆，我的弗拉圖拉語很流利！
I'm fluent in Flatula, Jim.

285
00:17:37,303 --> 00:17:38,930
我在大學裏學了兩年！
Took two years of it in high school.

286
00:17:40,406 --> 00:17:43,203
弗拉圖拉？太酷了！
Flatula? Cool.

287
00:17:44,508 --> 00:17:47,500
早上好，船長！ 都準備好了嗎？
Good morning, Captain. Everything shipshape?

288
00:17:47,545 --> 00:17:51,173
都準備好了，先生！ 但是我不是船長！
Shipshape it is, sir, but I'm not the captain.

289
00:17:51,214 --> 00:17:53,044
船長在上面！
The captain's aloft.

290
00:18:00,021 --> 00:18:02,216
埃柔先生，我已經
Mr. Arrow, I've checked

291
00:18:02,257 --> 00:18:06,692
上上下下檢查過了
from stem to stern,

292
00:18:06,726 --> 00:18:08,750
你怎麼都不會出點錯？
Can you get nothing wrong?

293
00:18:08,796 --> 00:18:11,160
您過講了，船長
You flatter me, Captain.

294
00:18:12,998 --> 00:18:16,093
啊，多普勒博士，我沒認錯吧？
Ah, Dr. Doppler, I presume?

295
00:18:16,135 --> 00:18:17,930
哦，是的，我...
Uh, um, yes. I--

296
00:18:17,969 --> 00:18:21,200
-你好啊，你能聽到我說話嗎？ -是的，我可以，不要再敲了！
-Hello! Can you hear me? -Yes, I can! Stop that banging!

297
00:18:21,238 --> 00:18:23,900
博士，這東西使用時
If I may, Doctor, this works so much better...

298
00:18:23,940 --> 00:18:26,067
可以工作的更好
when it's right-way up and plugged in.

299
00:18:26,109 --> 00:18:28,236
-哦！ -你真是太可愛了！
-Ooh! -Lovely. There you go.

300
00:18:28,278 --> 00:18:30,905
您要是不介意， 我想我可以自己來控制
If you don't mind, I can manage my own plugging!

301
00:18:30,946 --> 00:18:32,071
我是阿米莉婭船長
I'm Captain Amelia...

302
00:18:32,113 --> 00:18:33,916
普洛騰艦隊的後起之秀
Iate of a few run-ins with the Protean armada.

303
00:18:33,916 --> 00:18:36,110
齷齪的買賣， 但我不想因我的創傷煩擾你
Nasty business, but I won't bore you with my scars.

304
00:18:36,150 --> 00:18:37,914
您已經見過我的助手了 ——埃柔先生
You've met my first officer, Mr. Arrow.

305
00:18:37,952 --> 00:18:40,045
淳樸，強壯，可靠， 誠實，勇猛，忠實
Sterling, tough, dependable, honest, brave, and true.

306
00:18:40,088 --> 00:18:41,712
行了，船長
Please, Captain.

307
00:18:41,753 --> 00:18:43,721
哦，閉嘴，埃柔！ 我是說你一樣都不是
Oh, shut up, Arrow. You know I don't mean a word of it.

308
00:18:43,755 --> 00:18:47,122
啊哈，打擾一下。 我不喜歡打斷人家！
Ahem, excuse me. I hate to interrupt. It's not much better.

309
00:18:47,158 --> 00:18:49,626
但是，我可以跟你們介紹， 吉姆·霍金斯
but may I introduce to you, Jim Hawkins?

310
00:18:49,660 --> 00:18:52,959
吉姆，你們知道， 就是找到那些珍寶的男孩
Jim, you see, is the boy who found the treasure--

311
00:18:52,997 --> 00:18:55,157
博士，夠了！
Doctor, please!

312
00:18:57,768 --> 00:19:00,234
到我船艙來， 我跟你談談
I'd like a word with you in my stateroom.

313
00:19:01,469 --> 00:19:06,930
博士，在這些多嘴的人面前
Doctor, to muse and blabber about the treasure now

314
00:19:06,974 --> 00:19:08,943
說這些關於財寶的事情
in front of this particular crew...

315
00:19:08,976 --> 00:19:11,205
只能說明
demonstrates a level of ineptitude...

316
00:19:11,244 --> 00:19:13,403
你簡直就是一個低能兒
that borders on the imbecilic...

317
00:19:13,445 --> 00:19:15,437
這麼說，我已經是很人道了
and I mean that in a very caring way.

318
00:19:15,481 --> 00:19:18,938
低能？你這麼說我？ 愚蠢，我..
Imbecilic, did you say? Foolishness, I've--

319
00:19:18,984 --> 00:19:20,609
我可以看看地圖嗎？
May I see the map, please?

320
00:19:26,290 --> 00:19:27,449
看吧
Here.

321
00:19:29,058 --> 00:19:31,491
呣，太好了
Hmm. Fascinating.

322
00:19:33,195 --> 00:19:35,162
霍金斯先生，以後
Mr. Hawkins, in the future...

323
00:19:35,196 --> 00:19:37,096
你可以叫我「船長」或者是「先生」
you will address me as "Captain" or "Ma'am."

324
00:19:37,132 --> 00:19:38,258
明白了嗎？
Is that clear?

325
00:19:38,299 --> 00:19:40,768
啊
Ugh...

326
00:19:40,802 --> 00:19:42,097
霍金斯先生？
Mr. Hawkins?

327
00:19:43,137 --> 00:19:46,104
-知道了，先生
-Yes, ma'am.

328
00:19:46,139 --> 00:19:49,097
先生們，這東西不用的時候， 我們必須把它鎖起來
Gentlemen, this must be kept under lock and key...

329
00:19:49,097 --> 00:19:52,970
博士，我用我最誠摯的敬意 再說一遍
when not in use. And, Doctor, again...with the greatest possible respect...

330
00:19:53,009 --> 00:19:55,034
不要再大聲嚷嚷！
zip your howling screamer.

331
00:19:55,079 --> 00:19:56,740
船長，我保證
Captain, I assure you l--

332
00:19:56,782 --> 00:20:00,272
我簡短的說一下
Let me make this as monosyllabic as possible.

333
00:20:00,316 --> 00:20:04,616
我不在乎你僱用的這些水手
I don't much care for this crew you hired.

334
00:20:04,654 --> 00:20:07,054
他們...埃柔， 你說我要怎麼形容這些人？
They're...how did l describe them, Arrow?

335
00:20:07,089 --> 00:20:09,420
早茶之前我說得很清楚了
I said something rather good this morning before coffee.

336
00:20:09,458 --> 00:20:13,757
「一幫滑稽可笑的留著口水的傻子！」先生
"A ludicrous parcel of driveling galoots," ma'am.

337
00:20:13,795 --> 00:20:17,320
-就是這樣！太有詩意了！ -現在，看著我
-There you go--poetry. -Now, see here--

338
00:20:17,363 --> 00:20:21,526
博士，我想和所有的船員聊天
Doctor, I'd love to chat to the whole ship crew.

339
00:20:21,567 --> 00:20:22,897
但是，我得負責這艘船的航行
but I have a ship to launch...

340
00:20:22,934 --> 00:20:25,036
你也擦亮了你的裝備
and you've got your outfit to buff up.

341
00:20:25,035 --> 00:20:27,366
埃柔先生，請你把這兩個新人
Mr. Arrow, please escort these two neophytes...

342
00:20:27,404 --> 00:20:28,928
帶下去
down to the galley straightaway.

343
00:20:28,973 --> 00:20:31,702
年輕的霍金斯就跟著 我們的廚師席爾瓦先生
Young Hawkins will be working for our cook, Mr. Silver.

344
00:20:31,742 --> 00:20:34,175
什麼？廚師？
What? The cook?

345
00:20:35,547 --> 00:20:38,016
死女人，屬貓的！
That woman! That...feline!

346
00:20:38,050 --> 00:20:40,245
她搞清楚誰才是頭兒了沒有？
Who does she think is working for whom?

347
00:20:40,286 --> 00:20:42,616
那是我的地圖， 她是拿我的工錢的！
It's my map, and she's got me bussin' tables?

348
00:20:42,653 --> 00:20:45,383
不許你們說我船長的壞話！
I'll not tolerate a cross word about our captain!

349
00:20:45,422 --> 00:20:49,755
再也找不到比她更好的長官了！
There's no finer officer in this or any galaxy.

350
00:20:52,728 --> 00:20:54,855
席爾瓦先生？
Mr. Silver?

351
00:20:54,897 --> 00:20:57,127
怎麼了？埃柔先生？
Why, Mr. Arrow, sir.

352
00:20:57,165 --> 00:20:59,564
您的到來
Bringin' in such fine and distinguished gents...

353
00:20:59,600 --> 00:21:01,567
使這裏蓬蓽生輝
to grace my humble galley.

354
00:21:01,602 --> 00:21:04,070
您有何指示？
Had I known,

355
00:21:04,105 --> 00:21:05,535
呵呵呵呵
Heh heh heh heh!

356
00:21:08,607 --> 00:21:10,574
機器人！
A cyborg!

357
00:21:10,609 --> 00:21:12,839
這是多普勒博士！
May I introduce Dr. Doppler?

358
00:21:12,876 --> 00:21:15,276
我們此次航行的投資者
The financier of our voyage.

359
00:21:15,313 --> 00:21:17,439
博士，您裝備很可愛
Lovely outfit, Doc.

360
00:21:17,480 --> 00:21:21,008
哦，謝謝！ 您的眼睛也很不錯！
Well, thank you. Um, lovely eye.

361
00:21:21,051 --> 00:21:23,780
這個小傢伙是吉姆·霍金斯
Uh, this young lad is Jim Hawkins.

362
00:21:24,885 --> 00:21:26,978
吉姆！哦...
Jimbo! Uh...

363
00:21:31,158 --> 00:21:35,787
啊，不要被這大傢伙嚇著了
Aw, now, don't be too put off by this hunk of hardware.

364
00:21:42,199 --> 00:21:43,792
哇！
Whoa!

365
00:21:43,835 --> 00:21:46,098
這裝置可以用來...
These gears have been tough getting used to...

366
00:21:46,137 --> 00:21:49,903
但是他們的確很方便
but they do come in mighty handy from time to time.

367
00:21:57,947 --> 00:21:59,674
呣！
Mmm!

368
00:21:59,713 --> 00:22:04,810
好了，來，嘗嘗！
Here, now, have a taste

369
00:22:07,721 --> 00:22:07,920
呣！我喜歡這味道， 濃烈的味道
Mmm! Delightfully tangy, yet robust.

370
00:22:07,919 --> 00:22:11,547
呣！我喜歡這味道， 濃烈的味道
Mmm! Delightfully tangy, yet robust.

371
00:22:11,590 --> 00:22:14,150
祖傳秘方！
Old family recipe.

372
00:22:14,192 --> 00:22:15,283
啊！
Aah!

373
00:22:15,326 --> 00:22:18,954
實際上，那是祖傳秘方中的一部分！
In fact, that was part of the old family!

374
00:22:18,996 --> 00:22:21,965
哈哈哈哈！
Ha ha ha!

375
00:22:21,999 --> 00:22:25,024
歐歐歐！博士，我只是開個玩笑！
Oh, ho! I'm just kiddin', Doc!

376
00:22:25,068 --> 00:22:26,398
哦，是的，沒事
Uh, yeah, well...

377
00:22:26,435 --> 00:22:28,960
我要不開玩笑， 那不就是我了
I'm nothin' if I ain't a kidder.

378
00:22:29,004 --> 00:22:31,495
喝吧，吉姆！
Go on, Jimbo. Have a swig.

379
00:22:39,012 --> 00:22:40,172
墨菲！
Morph!

380
00:22:40,213 --> 00:22:43,476
你這個淘氣的水滴！
You jiggle-headed blob of mischief!

381
00:22:43,515 --> 00:22:46,007
你剛才藏哪兒去了？
So that's where you was hiding!

382
00:22:50,722 --> 00:22:53,517
哇！哈！ 這是什麼？
Wha--? Ha! What is that thing?

383
00:22:53,555 --> 00:22:54,888
「這是什麼？」
"What is that thing?"

384
00:22:54,925 --> 00:22:56,722
他是個變種！
He's a morph.

385
00:22:56,760 --> 00:22:59,728
我在變體1中裝了形狀轉換裝備
I rescued the little shape-shifter on Proteus 1.

386
00:23:01,328 --> 00:23:03,889
啊哈，他看上我了
Aw, he took a shine to me.

387
00:23:03,933 --> 00:23:06,695
我們一直在一起
We been together ever since.

388
00:23:06,734 --> 00:23:09,566
好極了，啊，乖孩子
Right? Yeah. Nice boy.

389
00:23:09,602 --> 00:23:11,001
走吧，我們下去吧
We're about to get underway.

390
00:23:11,037 --> 00:23:13,163
博士，您要不要參觀一下這艘飛船？
Would you like to observe the launch, doctor?

391
00:23:13,205 --> 00:23:14,434
我可以嗎？
Would l?

392
00:23:14,473 --> 00:23:18,134
現在的星系核有超光速飛機嗎？
Does an active galactic nucleus have superluminal jets?

393
00:23:18,176 --> 00:23:20,541
你帶路！
I'll follow you.

394
00:23:20,578 --> 00:23:24,376
席爾瓦先生， 霍金斯先生留在這裏聽你的指示！
Mr. Hawkins will stay here in your charge, Mr. Silver.

395
00:23:25,582 --> 00:23:27,881
先生，您能再說一遍嗎？
Beggin' your pardon, sir, but--

396
00:23:27,919 --> 00:23:32,820
這是船長的命令， 別讓這個新來的服務生閒著！
Captain's orders! See to it the new cabin boy's kept busy.

397
00:23:32,855 --> 00:23:35,618
-啊，但是不行...
-Aw, but, no, but--

398
00:23:40,094 --> 00:23:44,052
這樣，船長讓你和我在一起？
So, Captain's put you with me, eh?

399
00:23:44,096 --> 00:23:45,962
不管怎麼樣
Whatever.

400
00:23:45,997 --> 00:23:51,400
我一個低賤的機器人 是不能和船長爭論的
Well, who be a humble cyborg to argue with a captain?

401
00:23:51,436 --> 00:23:53,734
是的
Yeah.

402
00:23:53,771 --> 00:23:56,763
你知道的，這些小狗
You know...these purps...

403
00:23:56,807 --> 00:24:01,072
他們就像是 從蒙特裏莎回來的一樣
they're kind of like the ones back home on Montressor.

404
00:24:01,109 --> 00:24:02,703
你去過那兒？
You ever been there?

405
00:24:02,746 --> 00:24:05,406
吉姆，不能說是我去過
I can't say as I have, Jimbo.

406
00:24:06,982 --> 00:24:09,643
仔細想想
Come to think of it,

407
00:24:09,684 --> 00:24:11,709
我碰到這個老傢伙
I met this old guy, who was, um...

408
00:24:11,753 --> 00:24:15,118
他在找他的機器人夥伴
he was kind of looking for a cyborg buddy of his.

409
00:24:15,155 --> 00:24:16,452
是嗎？
Is that so?

410
00:24:16,489 --> 00:24:17,819
是的
Yeah.

411
00:24:17,857 --> 00:24:21,690
那人叫什麼名字？
What was that old salamander's name?

412
00:24:21,727 --> 00:24:24,217
哦，哦，鮑恩斯
Oh, yeah. Bones.

413
00:24:24,262 --> 00:24:26,196
比利·鮑恩斯？
Billy Bones?

414
00:24:26,230 --> 00:24:29,323
鮑恩斯？鮑恩斯？
Bones? Bones?!

415
00:24:29,366 --> 00:24:31,663
呣，他有搖鈴嗎？
Mm-mmm. T'ain't ringin' any bells.

416
00:24:31,701 --> 00:24:33,965
一定是另外一個機器人！
Must have been a different cyborg.

417
00:24:34,003 --> 00:24:37,267
在這艘船上還有許多機器人
There's a slew of cyborgs roamin' this port.

418
00:24:38,506 --> 00:24:40,236
準備起飛！
Prepare to cast off!

419
00:24:40,276 --> 00:24:44,210
哦，去吧，小伙子， 去看看起飛吧
Eh, off with you, lad, and watch the launch.

420
00:24:44,244 --> 00:24:48,180
還有許多工作等著你做呢
There'll be plenty work a-waitin' for you afterwards.

421
00:24:52,485 --> 00:24:58,786
我們最好盯著這個男孩， 是不是，墨菲？
We best be keepin' a sharp eye on this one, eh, Morph?

422
00:24:58,822 --> 00:25:03,726
我們不能讓他多管閒事！
We wouldn't want him strayin' into things he shouldn't.

423
00:25:03,834 --> 00:25:06,960
船長，我們都準備好了
We're all clear, Captain!

424
00:25:07,002 --> 00:25:10,334
哦，朋友， 我們是不是可以讓這破船起飛了？
Well, my friend. Are we ready to raise this creaking tub?

425
00:25:10,372 --> 00:25:12,463
船長，榮幸之至！
My pleasure, Captain.

426
00:25:12,506 --> 00:25:15,497
各就各位！
All hands to stations!

427
00:25:16,743 --> 00:25:17,868
快點！
Smartly now!

428
00:25:17,910 --> 00:25:19,468
快點，你這個渣仔！ 我要追上你！
Come on, you scurvy scum! I'll race you!

429
00:25:23,248 --> 00:25:26,478
打開所有太陽能帆！
Loose all solar sails!

430
00:25:31,587 --> 00:25:32,747
快！
Come on!

431
00:25:37,626 --> 00:25:40,686
把帆拉緊！
Heave up the braces.

432
00:25:40,729 --> 00:25:42,525
拉緊！
Brace up.

433
00:25:56,942 --> 00:25:58,636
哦，哦！
Ooh. Oh.

434
00:25:58,676 --> 00:26:01,576
佐夫先生，加強船的吸引力
Mr. Zoff, engage the dropt

435
00:26:09,119 --> 00:26:12,449
騰巴克先生，南偏西， 轉向：2－1－0－0
South by southwest, Mr. Turnbuckle, heading 2-1-0-0.

436
00:26:12,486 --> 00:26:15,354
是，船長。2－1－0－0
Aye, Captain. 2-1-0-0.

437
00:26:17,724 --> 00:26:19,918
全速前進。埃柔先生！
Full speed, Mr. Arrow, if you please.

438
00:26:19,960 --> 00:26:21,257
全速前進！
Take her away!

439
00:26:25,231 --> 00:26:27,357
博士，您能不能堅強一點？
Brace yourself, Doctor.

440
00:26:27,398 --> 00:26:29,365
「您能不能堅強一點？」
"Brace yourself."

441
00:26:29,399 --> 00:26:31,391
啊！哦！
Aah! Oof!

442
00:26:50,617 --> 00:26:51,744
哇！
Whoa.

443
00:27:08,365 --> 00:27:12,596
難以置信 這就是冥界的銀河？
Upon my word, an Orcus Galacticus.

444
00:27:14,302 --> 00:27:15,599
笑一個
Smile.

445
00:27:15,637 --> 00:27:17,195
哦，博士，你最好站遠點
Uh, Doctor, I'd stand clear--

446
00:27:20,508 --> 00:27:22,032
哈
Ha.

447
00:27:22,076 --> 00:27:25,101
啊，船長 真是航運史上一個偉大的日子
Ah. 'tis a grand day for sailing. Captain...

448
00:27:25,144 --> 00:27:26,577
看看您
and look at you.

449
00:27:26,612 --> 00:27:29,239
您衣冠楚楚，就像
You're as trim and as bonny as a sloop...

450
00:27:29,281 --> 00:27:32,078
一艘上了新帆， 塗了新漆的帆船
with new sails and a fresh coat of paint.

451
00:27:32,117 --> 00:27:33,948
席爾瓦先生， 你可以把你的這些恭維
You can keep that kind of flim-flammery...

452
00:27:33,986 --> 00:27:35,850
送給那些在空間站的妓女
for your spaceport floozies, Silver.

453
00:27:35,887 --> 00:27:37,353
飛船基地的妓女 飛船基地的妓女
Spaceport floozy, spaceport floozy--

454
00:27:37,388 --> 00:27:39,789
船長，你也太打擊我了
You cut me to the quick, Captain.

455
00:27:39,824 --> 00:27:42,758
我一直有什麼說什麼
I speaks nothing but me heart at all times.

456
00:27:42,792 --> 00:27:44,019
自是肺腑之言
Nothing but me heart.

457
00:27:44,058 --> 00:27:46,856
對了，那是你的幫手嗎？
And, by the way, isn't that your cabin boy...

458
00:27:46,896 --> 00:27:50,591
在桅桿上閒逛的？
aimlessly footling about in those shrouds?

459
00:27:50,631 --> 00:27:52,258
是的，他...哦
Yep, it--oh...

460
00:27:52,300 --> 00:27:57,327
只是一時的失誤，船長！ 馬上就會恢復正常！吉姆！
A momentary aberration, Cap'n, soon to be addressed. Jimbo!

461
00:27:58,804 --> 00:28:01,600
我新交了兩個朋友， 我想你見見他們
I got two new friends I'd like you to meet.

462
00:28:03,042 --> 00:28:07,943
跟拖把先生和水桶小姐問好吧
Say hello to Mr. Mop and Mrs. Bucket.

463
00:28:07,977 --> 00:28:09,912
呵呵呵呵！
Heh heh heh heh!

464
00:28:09,947 --> 00:28:11,277
好啊
Yippee.

465
00:28:13,217 --> 00:28:15,047
好了，我認識拖把先生了
Yeah, I got your Mr. Mop.

466
00:28:18,253 --> 00:28:21,050
小心點，笨蛋
Watch it, twerp.

467
00:28:34,899 --> 00:28:37,561
看什麼看，怪物！
What are you looking at, weirdo?

468
00:28:38,836 --> 00:28:40,995
就是，怪物
Yeah, weirdo.

469
00:28:44,508 --> 00:28:51,138
服務生要學會 專心干自己的事！
Cabin boys should learn to mind their own business.

470
00:28:51,179 --> 00:28:53,670
為什麼？你把什麼東西藏起來了？ 亮眼睛的傢伙？
Why? You got something to hide, bright eyes?

471
00:28:55,250 --> 00:28:59,947
看來你的耳朵有問題
Maybe your ears don't work so well.

472
00:28:59,986 --> 00:29:01,955
是的，啊
Yeah. Ahem.

473
00:29:01,988 --> 00:29:04,014
壞透了， 但是我的鼻子卻很正常
Too bad my nose works just fine.

474
00:29:04,058 --> 00:29:08,048
什麼！你這個沒有家教的傢伙！
Why, you impudent little--

475
00:29:10,062 --> 00:29:11,824
繼續，把他剁了！
Go ahead! Slice him! Dice him!

476
00:29:13,731 --> 00:29:17,825
你再說一遍？服務生！
Any last words, cabin boy?

477
00:29:20,169 --> 00:29:21,534
斯科洛先生
Mr. Scroop...

478
00:29:24,204 --> 00:29:27,037
你知道
you ever see what happens to a fresh purp...

479
00:29:27,075 --> 00:29:30,942
狗被用力掐的下場嗎？
when you squeeze real hard?

480
00:29:33,145 --> 00:29:34,611
出什麼事了！
What's all this. then?

481
00:29:38,117 --> 00:29:39,948
你們知道規矩的
You know the rules.

482
00:29:39,986 --> 00:29:42,612
船上不許大聲喧嘩
There'll be no brawling on this ship.

483
00:29:42,654 --> 00:29:43,847
是的，是的，先生
Aye, aye, sir.

484
00:29:43,887 --> 00:29:47,583
以後誰要再犯，
Any further offenders will be confined to the brig...

485
00:29:47,625 --> 00:29:50,387
就只能呆在狹窄的雙桅船裏了
for the remainder of the voyage.

486
00:29:50,425 --> 00:29:54,054
斯科洛先生， 我說得夠明白嗎？
Am I clear, Mr. Scroop?

487
00:29:59,767 --> 00:30:02,201
知道了
Transparently.

488
00:30:07,673 --> 00:30:10,469
做的好，埃柔先生！
Well done, Mr. Arrow, sir!

489
00:30:10,507 --> 00:30:13,375
一艘團結的船， 一艘令人愉快的船！
A tight ship's a happy ship, sir.

490
00:30:14,544 --> 00:30:17,273
吉姆，給你個活幹！
Jimbo, I gave you a job.

491
00:30:17,314 --> 00:30:19,715
嘿，之前我一直在做！
Hey, I was doing it until that bug thing--

492
00:30:19,750 --> 00:30:24,912
閉嘴， 現在我要你把甲板拖的乾乾淨淨
Belay that! Now, I want this deck swabbed spotless...

493
00:30:24,953 --> 00:30:28,513
我回來之前還沒做好， 你就祈求上帝保佑吧
and heaven help you if I come back and it's not done.

494
00:30:28,555 --> 00:30:32,253
墨菲， 看著這小子
Morph? Keep an eye on this pup...

495
00:30:32,293 --> 00:30:34,920
隨時留意著他有沒有分心
and let me know if there be any more distractions.

496
00:30:34,962 --> 00:30:36,120
是，遵命！
OK. Aye-aye.

497
00:30:45,233 --> 00:30:47,563
好了，大家都到齊了
So, we're all here, then.

498
00:30:47,600 --> 00:30:50,832
-來了 -很好
-Excuse me. -Fine.

499
00:30:52,204 --> 00:30:57,335
先生們，請原諒我的坦率
Now, if you pardon my plain speaking, gentlemen...

500
00:30:57,376 --> 00:30:59,036
你們都是
are you all...

501
00:30:59,078 --> 00:31:02,775
笨蛋， 徹徹底底的蠢貨嗎！？
stark-raving, totally blinking daft?!

502
00:31:04,082 --> 00:31:06,344
我好不容易讓大家
After all me finagling getting us hired...

503
00:31:06,382 --> 00:31:08,009
以水手的身份上船
as an upstanding crew...

504
00:31:08,051 --> 00:31:11,816
你們想讓計劃全部敗露嗎？
you want to blow the whole mutiny before it's time?

505
00:31:11,854 --> 00:31:14,822
那男孩已經有所察覺了！
The boy was sniffing about.

506
00:31:14,857 --> 00:31:20,452
是你差點讓計劃失敗的，笨蛋！
You just stick to the plan, you bug-brained twit.

507
00:31:20,494 --> 00:31:24,190
至於那個小孩， 我會給他一堆的活兒
As for the boy, I'll run him so ragged...

508
00:31:24,229 --> 00:31:26,288
讓他沒有時間去想
he won't have time to think.

509
00:31:36,873 --> 00:31:39,501
這真是有趣的一天
Well, this has been a fun day

510
00:31:39,542 --> 00:31:44,000
交了新朋友，像那個蜘蛛
Making new friends like that spider psycho.

511
00:31:44,045 --> 00:31:45,979
蜘蛛，蜘蛛
Spider psycho, spider psycho.

512
00:31:46,014 --> 00:31:47,844
呵呵，有點醜
Heh. A little uglier.

513
00:31:47,882 --> 00:31:50,315
哈哈哈哈
Mwah-ha-ha-ha!

514
00:31:50,350 --> 00:31:51,579
閉上嘴吧
Pretty close.

515
00:31:51,620 --> 00:31:52,879
哦
Well...

516
00:31:52,919 --> 00:31:55,910
這真要感謝上帝了
thank heavens for little miracles.

517
00:31:55,955 --> 00:31:57,547
上來一個小時了
Up here for an hour...

518
00:31:57,591 --> 00:31:59,888
